d-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Reign</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nMern of House Gardener, the Ninth of His Name</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\nPrince <a href=\"/index.php/Edmund_Gardener\" title=\"Edmund Gardener\">Edmund Gardener</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\nNone</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_2_Before_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">2&#160;BC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Fire\" title=\"Field of Fire\">Field of Fire</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nPrince <a href=\"/index.php/Edmund_Gardener\" title=\"Edmund Gardener\">Edmund Gardener</a><br />Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Gardener\" title=\"Gawen Gardener\">Gawen Gardener</a><br />Two unnamed sons</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Mern IX Gardener</b> was the last <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He and King <a href=\"/index.php/Loren_I_Lannister\" title=\"Loren I Lannister\">Loren I Lannister</a> are remembered collectively as the <a href=\"/index.php/Two_Kings\" title=\"Two Kings\">Two Kings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mern_IX_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cb/Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg/250px-Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"520\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cb/Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg/375px-Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cb/Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg/500px-Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mern_IX_Gardener_by_Peteryeeter.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Mern, by Peteryeeter</div></div></div>\n<p>After <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon the Conqueror</a> landed in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, set on <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">conquering</a> the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>. King Mern IX of <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">the Reach</a> and King <a href=\"/index.php/Loren_I_Lannister\" title=\"Loren I Lannister\">Loren I Lannister</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">the Rock</a> agreed to join forces and throw the invaders back into the sea. The two armies gathered near <a href=\"/index.php/Goldengrove\" title=\"Goldengrove\">Goldengrove</a> in the Reach. Since he had brought half as many more men, Mern had the honor of commanding the center of the combined army from the Reach and the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Edmund_Gardener\" title=\"Edmund Gardener\">Edmund</a>, Mern's son and heir, was to lead the vanguard, while another son, <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Gardener\" title=\"Gawen Gardener\">Gawen</a>, accompanied the king with the banner.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Mern led the charge against Aegon's army alongside his kin. The combined might of the Reach and the Rock began to break the Targaryen host, but Aegon and his sisters, <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenys_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenys Targaryen\">Rhaenys</a>, took to the sky with their <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>. The beasts killed 4,000 men of the combined army at the <a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Fire\" title=\"Field of Fire\">Field of Fire</a>, among them Mern and his sons, grandsons, brothers, uncles, cousins, and other kin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_landing_and_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_landing_and_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Another thousand men perished from sword and spears and arrows. One nephew of King Mern survived, but he died of his burns three days later, ending House Gardener.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mern_IX_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Our iron fist.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;King Mern IX Gardener boasting of his forces ahead of the Field of Fire</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mern_IX_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font